'''2009年印度尼西亞總統選舉'''於2009年7月8日舉行，如有需要，決選會於9月8日舉行<ref>{{cite news | last = Yang | first = Lina | title = Indonesia's presidential election day set at July 8 | url = http://news.xinhuanet.com/english/2009-01/23/content_10706882.htm | publisher = Xinhua | date = 2009-01-23 | accessdate = 2009-05-16 | archive-date = 2012-11-06 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20121106083217/http://news.xinhuanet.com/english/2009-01/23/content_10706882.htm | dead-url = no }}</ref>。當選的總統及副總統任期為2009年至2014年。根據印尼國家選舉委員會初步開票結果，現任總統[[蘇西洛·班邦·尤多約諾|尤多約諾]]得票起過六成，預計毋須決選便可以順利當選，正式的選舉結果將於7月底公布<ref>{{cite news| author =楊明娟| title =印尼官方初步開票顯示 尤多約諾贏得總統大選| url =http://news.rti.org.tw/index_newsContent.aspx?nid=205424| publisher =[[台灣中央廣播電台|台灣中央廣播電台]]| date =2009-07-09| accessdate =2009-07-12| deadurl =yes| archiveurl =https://archive.is/20120713153716/http://news.rti.org.tw/index_newsContent.aspx?nid=205424| archivedate =2012-07-13}}</ref>。

2009年7月24日，印尼选举委员会宣布，苏西洛·班邦·尤多约诺以60.8%的得票率，成功连任总统。

== 背景 ==

今次選舉是[[印尼|印尼]]第二次總統及副總統的全民直選。2004年，[[蘇西洛·班邦·尤多約諾|尤多約諾]]在決選中，擊敗當時在任的[[梅加瓦蒂·蘇加諾普翠|梅加瓦蒂]]。

2009年2月，現任副總統[[優素福·卡爾拉|卡拉]]宣佈不會成為[[蘇西洛·班邦·尤多約諾|尤多約諾]]的副手參選人，並表明，如果他擔任主席的[[專業集團黨|專業集團黨]]提名他為總統參選人，他願意挑戰尤多約諾。

其他有意參選人包括前總統[[阿卜杜勒-拉赫曼·瓦希德|瓦希德]]<ref>{{cite news | title = Abdurrahman Wahid plans new bid for Indonesian presidency | url = http://www.radioaustralia.net.au/news/stories/200807/s2306076.htm | publisher = [[Radio_Australia|Radio Australia]] | date = 2008-07-17 | accessdate = 2009-05-17 | archive-date = 2008-10-11 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20081011054600/http://www.radioaustralia.net.au/news/stories/200807/s2306076.htm | dead-url = no }}</ref>、前人民代表會議議長[[阿克巴爾·丹戎|丹戎]]<ref>{{cite news | title = Akbar Tanjung ready to join next year's presidential election | url = http://www.antara.co.id/en/arc/2008/5/25/akbar-tanjung-ready-to-join-next-years-presidential-election/ | publisher = [[ANTARA|ANTARA]] | date = 2008-05-25 | accessdate = 2009-05-17 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090414115826/http://antara.co.id/en/arc/2008/5/25/akbar-tanjung-ready-to-join-next-years-presidential-election/ | archivedate = 2009-04-14 }}</ref>、[[日惹|日惹]]蘇丹兼日惹特區省長[[哈孟庫布沃諾十世|哈孟庫布沃諾十世]]<ref>{{cite news | title = Indonesian sultan to run for president | url = http://www.antara.co.id/en/arc/2008/10/29/indonesian-sultan-to-run-for-president/ | publisher = [[ANTARA|ANTARA]] | date = 2008-10-29 | accessdate = 2009-05-17 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://archive.is/20120903230814/http://www.antara.co.id/en/arc/2008/10/29/indonesian-sultan-to-run-for-president/ | archivedate = 2012-09-03 }}</ref> 及前[[雅加達|雅加達]]首都特區省長[[蘇蒂約索|蘇蒂約索]]<ref>{{id icon}} {{cite news | title = Sutiyoso Berpeluang Besar Jika Cermat Pilih Cawapres | url = http://www.suaramerdeka.com/cybernews/harian/0710/02/nas6.htm | publisher = [[Suara_Merdeka_(newspaper)|Suara Merdeka]] | date = 2007-10-02 | accessdate = 2009-05-17 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090802074143/http://www.suaramerdeka.com/cybernews/harian/0710/02/nas6.htm | archivedate = 2009-08-02 }}</ref>。

2月17日，印尼憲法法庭裁定獨立人士不能參選<ref name="Pasandaran">{{cite news | first = Camelia | last = Pasandaran | script-title =en:Court Rules Out Independent Candidates for ’09 | publisher = [[Jakarta_Globe|Jakarta Globe]] | date = 2009-02-18 | accessdate = 2009-06-12}}</ref>。

== 政治結盟 ==

印尼立法議會選舉於4月9日舉行後，政黨開始結盟，提名參選人參選。根據2008年頒令的總統選舉法，參選人必須得到政黨或聯盟提名，而該政黨或聯盟需要在議會選舉中取得至少兩成半選票，或在人民代表議會取得至少兩成議席（按現時560名議員計算，參選人須得到112名議員支持）<ref>{{cite news | title = Many votes to count | url = http://www.economist.com/world/asia/displaystory.cfm?story_id=13448679 | publisher = [[The_Economist|The Economist]] | date = 2009-04-09 | accessdate = 2009-05-14 | archive-date = 2019-08-22 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190822023426/https://www.economist.com/asia/2009/04/09/many-votes-to-count | dead-url = no }}</ref>。印尼憲法法庭亦裁定獨立人士不能參選<ref name="Pasandaran"/>。有意參選者須於5月16日午夜前，到國家選舉委員會登記<ref>{{cite news | title = KPU urge presidential candidates to register before deadline passed | url = http://www.thejakartapost.com/news/2009/05/15/kpu-urge-presidential-candidates-register-deadline-passed.html | publisher = [[The_Jakarta_Post|The Jakarta Post]] | date = 2009-05-15 | accessdate = 2009-05-16 }}{{dead link|date=2017年11月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot }}</ref>。

有消息指，現任副總統[[優素福·卡爾拉|卡拉]]所屬的[[專業集團黨|專業集團黨]]會與前總統[[梅加瓦蒂·蘇加諾普翠|梅加瓦蒂]]所屬的[[民主奮鬥黨|民主奮鬥黨]]結盟，與[[蘇西洛·班邦·尤多約諾|尤多約諾]]的[[民主黨_(印尼)|民主黨]]競選。不過，兩黨談判於4月13日失敗，有指專業集團黨希望繼續與尤多約諾結盟，維持影響力。尤多約諾則與多個伊斯蘭團體會談，企圖結盟控制逾半國會議席<ref>{{cite news | first = Muklis | last = Ali | title = Indonesia president's party eyes Golkar, Islamist pact | url = http://www.reuters.com/article/worldNews/idUSTRE53C0QX20090413 | publisher = [[Reuters|Reuters]] | date = 2009-04-13 | accessdate = 2009-05-14 | archive-date = 2019-08-22 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190822023427/https://www.reuters.com/article/us-indonesia-election/indonesia-presidents-party-eyes-golkar-islamist-pact-idUSTRE53C0QX20090413 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | title = Democrat Party Exploring Coalition With Golkar | url = http://www.bernama.com/bernama/v5/newsworld.php?id=403756 | publisher = Bernama.com | date = 2009-04-13 | accessdate = 2009-05-14 | archive-date = 2016-03-03 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303194031/http://www.bernama.com/bernama/v5/newsworld.php?id=403756 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | title = Indonesia coalition talks 'near' | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/asia-pacific/7996419.stm | publisher = [[BBC|BBC]] | date = 2009-04-13 | accessdate = 2009-05-14 | archive-date = 2018-06-23 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180623062017/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/asia-pacific/7996419.stm | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

4月底，[[專業集團黨|專業集團黨]]與團體會晤，爭取提名[[優素福·卡爾拉|卡拉]]所需的選票。其後，一個由十個政黨組成的聯盟於5月1日成立，當中包括專業集團黨、[[民主奮鬥黨|民主奮鬥黨]]、[[大印尼行動黨|大印尼行動黨]]、[[人民良知黨|人民良知黨]]、[[和平福利黨|和平福利黨]]、[[改革星黨|改革星黨]]、[[全國教徒復興黨|全國教徒復興黨]]、[[全民關注黨|全民關注黨]]、[[印尼勞工黨|勞工黨]]及[[印尼回教教士黨|回教教士黨]]。[[民族使命黨|民族使命黨]]及[[統一建設黨|統一建設黨]]曾考慮參與，但最終沒有加入聯盟<ref>{{cite news | first = Dicky | last = Christanto | title = Political parties ink coalition agreement | url = http://www.thejakartapost.com/news/2009/05/01/political-parties-ink-coalition-agreement.html | publisher = [[The_Jakarta_Post|The Jakarta Post]] | date = 2009-05-01 | accessdate = 2009-05-14 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090513235508/http://www.thejakartapost.com/news/2009/05/01/political-parties-ink-coalition-agreement.html | archivedate = 2009-05-13 }}</ref>。十黨聯盟成立不久，[[優素福·卡爾拉|卡拉]]隨即宣布與前軍方領袖[[威蘭多|威蘭多]]合組名單參選<ref name="Kalla Wiranto">{{cite news | title = Indonesia's Kalla, Wiranto in presidency run | url = http://www.google.com/hostednews/afp/article/ALeqM5g_0mBYcrvaRhceoxYohK5I1GB4Gg | publisher = [[Agence_France-Presse|Agence France-Presse]] | date = 2009-05-01 | accessdate = 2009-05-14 | archive-date = 2012-09-06 | archive-url = https://archive.is/20120906221118/www.google.com/hostednews/afp/article/ALeqM5g_0mBYcrvaRhceoxYohK5I1GB4Gg | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

5月7日，[[民主奮鬥黨|民主奮鬥黨]]宣布前總統[[梅加瓦蒂·蘇加諾普翠|梅加瓦蒂]]參選，但未有公布副參選人<ref>{{cite news | title = Indonesia's PDIP Party officially nominates Megawati as presidential candidate | url = http://english.people.com.cn/90001/90777/90851/6653237.html | publisher = [[People's_Daily|People's Daily]] | date = 2009-05-07 | accessdate = 2009-05-14 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110606010832/http://english.people.com.cn/90001/90777/90851/6653237.html | archive-date = 2011-06-06 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>。民主奮鬥黨高層傾向[[大印尼行動黨|大印尼行動黨]]的[[普拉伯沃|普拉伯沃]]成為梅加瓦蒂副參選人，但兩黨於登記截止日（即5月16日）兩日前才達成共識<ref>{{cite news | first = Markus Junianto | last = Sihaloho | title = PDI-P to Announce Megawati's Mate | url = http://www.thejakartaglobe.com/news/national/article/18920.html | publisher = [[Jakarta_Globe|Jakarta Globe]] | date = 2009-05-02 | accessdate = 2009-05-14 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200328040154/https://jakartaglobe.id/news/national/article/18920.html | archive-date = 2020-03-28 | dead-url = yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | first = Markus Junianto | last = Sihaloho | author2 = Hutapea, Febriamy | title = Mega's Hopes Go Down to The Wire | url = http://www.thejakartaglobe.com/home/article/19860.html | publisher = [[Jakarta_Globe|Jakarta Globe]] | date = 2009-05-15 | accessdate = 2009-05-15 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090519035525/http://www.thejakartaglobe.com/home/article/19860.html | archivedate = 2009-05-19 }}</ref>，5月15日公布推舉梅加瓦蒂參選總統，普拉伯沃參選副總統。

十黨聯盟亦議定，假如[[優素福·卡爾拉|卡拉]]及[[梅加瓦蒂·蘇加諾普翠|梅加瓦蒂]]中其中一人未能成為總統參選人，其中一方亦須協助另一方競選，對抗[[蘇西洛·班邦·尤多約諾|尤多約諾]]<ref>{{cite news | last = Suhartono | title = JK-Win dan Mega-Pro Akan Saling Dukung | url = http://nasional.kompas.com/read/xml/2009/05/16/01083631/JK-Win.dan.Mega-Pro.Akan.Saling.Dukung | publisher = [[Kompas|Kompas]] | date = 2009-05-16 | accessdate = 2009-05-16 | archive-date = 2009-05-19 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20090519131055/http://nasional.kompas.com/read/xml/2009/05/16/01083631/JK-Win.dan.Mega-Pro.Akan.Saling.Dukung | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

5月12日，[[蘇西洛·班邦·尤多約諾|尤多約諾]]選[[印尼中央銀行|印尼中央銀行]]行長[[布迪奧諾|布迪奧諾]]為副參選人。與尤多約諾所屬的民主黨的聯盟，包括[[民族復興黨|民族復興黨]]、[[統一建設黨|統一建設黨]]及[[公正福利黨|公正福利黨]]，卻預期副參選人會選自其中一個聯盟黨。四個聯盟黨一度威脅與[[大印尼行動黨|大印尼行動黨]]結盟，另推一位參選人，不過民族復興黨後來對尤多約諾的做法表示支持<ref>{{cite news | title = President Susilo's party allies threaten to withdraw support | url = http://english.people.com.cn/90001/90777/90851/6656232.html | publisher = [[People's_Daily|People's Daily]] | date = 2009-05-12 | accessdate = 2009-05-16 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110606010854/http://english.people.com.cn/90001/90777/90851/6656232.html | archive-date = 2011-06-06 | dead-url = yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | title = PKB firm in its support for SBY-Boediono presidential ticket | url = http://www.antara.co.id/en/arc/2009/5/14/pkb-firm-in-its-support-for-sby-boediono-presidential-ticket/ | publisher = [[ANTARA|ANTARA]] | date = 2009-05-14 | accessdate = 2009-05-16 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090517052413/http://antara.co.id/en/arc/2009/5/14/pkb-firm-in-its-support-for-sby-boediono-presidential-ticket/ | archivedate = 2009-05-17 }}</ref>，其餘三個聯盟黨最後也唯有支持，並參與5月15日在[[萬隆|萬隆]]的提名典禮。不過，公正福利黨繼續與民主黨談判，要求尤多約諾一旦當選，權力要與公正福利黨更均勻地分配<ref>{{cite news | title = Islamic Allies Give Nod to SBY's Choice And Return to the Coalition Talks Table | url = http://www.thejakartaglobe.com/home/article/19990.html | publisher = [[Jakarta_Globe|Jakarta Globe]] | date = 2009-05-15 | accessdate = 2009-05-16 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090519183154/http://www.thejakartaglobe.com/home/article/19990.html | archivedate = 2009-05-19 }}</ref>。

